title: Diamond Crown Lounge Grand Opening!
itunes:title: Diamond Crown Lounge Grand Opening!
description: Eric Newman, President of JC Newman Cigar Company, joins The Cigar Authority for the grand opening of The Diamond Crown Cigar Lounge at Two Guys Smoke Shop in Nashua, NH. We light up the Diamond Crown #2, and the Julius Caeser.
